data.description: Nestled within the Kennesaw Battle condo community with its tree-lined streets and sidewalks youCOll find this meticulously maintained 3 bedroom 2 1/2 bath townhouse style home. This charming private gated community is close to the Kennesaw Mountain Battlefield park, shopping and dining. This home offers a 2-car detached garage, tranquil, private courtyard and easy access to guest parking. As you enter into the homes welcoming foyer to the right is the well equipped eat-in kitchen with bay window. The laundry is off the breakfast area. The kitchen offers gas cooking, plenty of counter space and natural tone cabinets. ThereCOs an open view to the fireside den. Attention to the detailed crown molding, hardwood floors and neutral paint brings a touch of class to the main level. Off the den enjoy relaxing in the private patio courtyard with covered access to the garage. Also on the main level is the half-bath and coat closet. The upper level offers two secondary bedrooms and a secondary bath with linen closet. The spacious Primary suite has a deep trace ceiling, bay window, walk-in closet, crown molding and private en-suite. New water heater. The community has a private pool, charming pool house and central mailbox location.
